Jill Dennett https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jill_Dennett 0 Jill Dennett (May 26, 1913 – 1941) was a motion picture actress in Hollywood movies for a decade, beginning in 1932. She appeared in more than twenty films, all of the appearances in uncredited roles. She was an attractive redhead who was also a talented dancer and singer. Born in New York and died in Surrey, England at age 27. Jill_Dennett ( May_26_,_1913 – 1941 ) was a_motion_picture_actress in Hollywood_movies for a_decade , beginning in 1932 .
